{"tid":2116851,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★展覽製作工程業半年零收入　從業員料五成公司將結業","createTime":"2020-07-20T12:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T13:45:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"21e4988ce1c6d7b863becdedc4d89d50ba280eb4","tid":2116851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"展覽製作工程業界代表陳啟恩指出，若沒有政府支援，估計將有五成展覽製作工程公司結業，約5,000人因此失業，影響數千個家庭生計。<br />\n<br />\n展覽製作工程人員關注組成員翁偉國將尋求進出口界立法會議員黃定光協助，聯同60多間公司成立「展覽製作工程人員解困關注組」，爭取政府在第三輪抗疫防疫基金支援業界渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/500348/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A5%AD%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%B6%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5-%E5%BE%9E%E6%A5%AD%E5%93%A1%E6%96%99%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B0%87%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F500348%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B1%2595%25E8%25A6%25BD%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%259B%25B6%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25A5-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=0810d337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/500348/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B1%95%E8%A6%BD%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%A5%AD%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E9%9B%B6%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5-%E5%BE%9E%E6%A5%AD%E5%93%A1%E6%96%99%E4%BA%94%E6%88%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%B0%87%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD</a>"},{"pid":"2930f84997b0558028bd7f4b49193b190db08665","tid":2116851,"uid":1891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:10:11.000Z"